<TITLE>Peter Applegarth</TITLE>
<TEXT>
Peter David Talbot Applegarth (born 8 August 1958) is a justice of the Supreme Court of Queensland in the Trial Division. He is a graduate of the law schools at both University of Queensland and Oxford University, and has served on the bench since 2008.


